Package: qtlr
Type: Package
Title: An Implementation of Quality Tolerance Limits
Version: 0.1.0.9001
Date: 2019-03-01
Authors@R: person("John", "Kirkpatrick", email = "john.kirkpatrick@roche.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: John Kirkpatrick <john.kirkpatrick@roche.com>
Description: An implementation of quality tolerance limits (QTLs) inspired by
    methodology presented by Berry et al (2010) in the context of meta analysis
    of clinical trials.  The binary methodology of Berry et al is extended to
    handle counts, time-to-event and continuous endpoints.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
